  [Text] Tokyo, June 23 KYODO -- Prime Minister Tsutomu Hata 
Thursday suggested he is ready to resign along with his entire 
cabinet if the current talks between his ruling coalition and 
the Social Democratic Party call for the step. 
  "I would like to leave (everything), including the issue of 
