<H3> <TI>   Japanese, U.S. Military `Tieup' Denounced </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Japanese, U.S. Military `Tieup' Denounced </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2306101094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1002 GMT 23 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2306101094 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Acts of Aggravating Northeast Asian Situation" -- KCNA </F>
headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, June 23 (KCNA) -- MINJU CHOSON today 
comments on the tightened tieup between Japan and the United 
States. 
  Recalling that U.S. Forces are planning to stage a joint 
commanding exercise with the "Self-Defence" Airforce of Japan at 
the airforce base in Florida, the analyst says: All the 
military moves are grave acts of carrying the situation of the 
Northeast Asian region including the Korean peninsula to the 
extreme pitch of strain. 
  The analyst notes: 
  It must not go unnoticed that the military collusion between 
Japan and the United States is being tightened when the United 
States and its followers are intensifying as never before their 
hostile moves to stifle the DPRK over its "nuclear issue". 
  The United States is advertising that the survey and 
selection of the bases of the Japanese "Self-Defence Forces" 
were "merely selection of shelters." But, in actuality, it is 
related to the preparations for a new war in Korea. 
  As everyone knows, the United States is massing its forces 
around the Korean peninsula, and Japan is frequently staging 
joint military exercises with the United States. These are very 
dangerous acts driving the situation in the Northeast Asian 
region to the brink of war. 
  The Korean people and other Northeast Asian peoples will not 
remain an onlooker to the acts of the United States and Japan 
aggravating the situation in this region. 
  The U.S. and Japanese authorities must renounce their 
military collusion and wild ambition for domination of Asia, as 
demanded by the Asian people. 

</TEXT>

