<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Seminars on Kim Chong-il's Works Held Abroad </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Seminars on Kim Chong-il's Works Held Abroad </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2006105294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1018 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2006105294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 20 (KCNA) -- A seminar on "1. The 
Origin of the Chuche Idea" from "On the Chuche Idea", a famous 
work of the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il, was held by the 
group for the study of the idea and theory of Comrade Kim 
Chong-il in Lebanon. 
  Saying that the chuche idea raised man's position and role 
in 
the world as the fundamental question of philosophy and 
elucidated the philosophical principle that man is the master of 
everything and decides everything, the reporter noted: "The 
Korean people have built a powerful socialist country of 
independence, self-sustenance and self-reliance in defence on 
the land of Korea on the basis of the chuche idea." 
  A seminar on the work "Our Socialism Centred on the Masses 
Shall Not Perish" was held at the Secretariat of the 
Agricultural Hydraulics of the Frelimo [Mozambique Liberation 
Front] Party of Mozambique. 
  Noting that Korea's socialism is strong because the leader, 
the party and the masses form a harmonious whole, speakers said: 
"The imperialists are trying to destroy the socialism of Korea, 
but it is a foolish dream." 
  A seminar on the work "Young Men and Women, Be the Vanguard 
Unfailingly Loyal to the Party and the Leader" was held at the 
society for the study of Kim Chong-il's works in Hwazana 
District, Harare Province, Zimbabwe. 

</TEXT>

