<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 23 (KCNA) -- The members of the 
home- visiting group of students of Korean university under the 
General Association of Korean Residents in Japan (Chongnyon) led 
by Ku Tae-sok, staying in the socialist homeland, Wednesday met 
with Yi In-mo, the incarnation of faith and will. 
  Referring to the harsh torture by the enemy in South Korea, 
he said he, however, refused to be converted and fought the 
enemy to the end, believing in only the great leader Comrade Kim 
