  [Text] Tokyo, June 24 KYODO -- Nippon Telegraph and 
Telephone Corp.'s purchases of equipment from foreign companies 
in fiscal 1993 ended last March were up 20.4 percent from the 
previous year to 119 billion yen, the telecommunications giant 
announced Friday [24 June]. 
